# 2. Why this structure is better

Because **gearsets are reusable components**.

Example:

```
ZF 8HP
```

contains:

```
planetary
planetary
planetary
planetary
```

connected with:

```
clutches
brakes
shafts
```

So your simulator should treat gearsets as **building blocks**.

